Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.08,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我的花朵曾昂然绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:16.95,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我曾光芒闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.85,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}可是太阳渐渐隐于地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.85,edchs,,0,0,25,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}一切都消失在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.25,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}梦中只剩下谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.09,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}唯我独醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:30.99,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an9\fad(150,200)}只剩内心的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.06,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an9\fad(150,200)}迷茫着走向黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:39.29,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我抛弃了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:44.49,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}只愿他们归来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:50.20,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我的一切  深爱过的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:53.19,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}都去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.55,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}给我些回应吧
Comment: 0,0:22:56.59,0:23:01.89,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur2\fad(150,200)}不知不觉  眼泪也流干了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:10.35,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我深爱的世界  已经回不来了
