Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.44,0:22:16.95,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}My outlook was shining
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.85,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}But the sun was shaded
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.85,edjp,,0,0,75,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}And they all vanished in the dark
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.25,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}夢が嘘を吐いて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.09,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}私を置き去って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.35,0:22:30.99,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}孤独を残して
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.06,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}迷い込んだ夜明け
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.41,0:22:39.29,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}何も要らない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.02,0:22:44.49,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}If only they'd come back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.75,0:22:50.20,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}My everything , my everything that I had loved
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.20,0:22:53.19,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}Where's everything?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.55,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}返事を聞かせてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.59,0:23:01.89,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}いつの間に涙さえも枯れていたわ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.26,0:23:10.35,edjp,,0,0,60,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}愛した世界が もうどこにもないから
